N2  - Professor Linda Argote of Carnegie Mellon University has been named the Editor-in-Chief of Organization Science, effective January 1, 2004. Until further notice, all new submissions should be sent to Professor Argote at CMU. See the below website at CMU for submission instructions: http://web.gsia.cmu.edu/orgsci/submission.htm
