N2  - This editorial describes the objectives of Organization Science and the kind of manuscripts that we hope to attract to the journal. Previous Editors-in-Chief are acknowledged and thanked for the excellent jobs they have done and for the superb reputation that the journal developed under their leadership. Incoming Senior Editors and members of the Editorial Review Board are introduced and welcomed. Ideas for continuing the traditions of innovation and excellence at Organization Science are discussed.
